{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"It is interesting that in the United States,"},{"time":3000,"text":"the most significant health-care budget"},{"time":5000,"text":"goes to cardiovascular disease care, whether it's private or public."},{"time":11000,"text":"There's no comparison at all."},{"time":14000,"text":"In Africa -- where it is a major killer -- it is totally ignored."}]},{"cues":[{"time":19000,"text":"And that situation cannot be right. We must do something about it."},{"time":25000,"text":"A health status of a nation parallels development of that nation."},{"time":31000,"text":"17 million people die every year from heart disease."},{"time":35000,"text":"32 million heart attacks and strokes occur."},{"time":38000,"text":"Most of this is in developing countries, and the majority is in Africa."},{"time":43000,"text":"85 percent of global disease burden for cardiovascular disease"},{"time":47000,"text":"is in developing countries -- not in the West --"},{"time":50000,"text":"and yet 90 percent of the resources are in the West."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55000,"text":"Who is at risk? People like you."},{"time":58000,"text":"It's not just the Africans that should be concerned about that."},{"time":61000,"text":"All friends of Africa, that will have reason to be in Africa at some point in time,"},{"time":67000,"text":"should be very concerned about this deplorable situation."},{"time":70000,"text":"Has anyone here wondered what will happen"},{"time":73000,"text":"if you go back to your room at night,"},{"time":75000,"text":"and you start getting chest pains, shortness of breath, sweating?"},{"time":79000,"text":"You're having a heart attack. What are you going to do?"},{"time":83000,"text":"Will you fly back to the U.S., Germany, Europe?"},{"time":88000,"text":"No, you will die. 50 percent will die within 24 hours, if not treated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93000,"text":"This is what's going on."},{"time":96000,"text":"In a look at the map of the U.S. -- the graph here,"},{"time":99000,"text":"10 million people here, 10 million here."},{"time":102000,"text":"By the time you get to 50, it's almost no one left in Nigeria --"},{"time":107000,"text":"life expectancy is 47."},{"time":109000,"text":"It's not because some people don't survive childhood illnesses --"},{"time":114000,"text":"they do -- but they do not survive after the time that they reach"},{"time":120000,"text":"about 45 years old and 50 years old."},{"time":124000,"text":"And those are the times they're most productive."},{"time":126000,"text":"Those are the times that they should be contributing"},{"time":128000,"text":"to Africa's development. But they're not there."},{"time":132000,"text":"The best way to spiral into a cycle of poverty is to kill the parents."},{"time":137000,"text":"If you cannot secure the parents,"},{"time":140000,"text":"you cannot guarantee the security of the African child."}]},{"cues":[{"time":142000,"text":"What are the risk factors?"},{"time":145000,"text":"It's very well known. I'm not going to spend a lot of time on those."},{"time":147000,"text":"These are just for information:"},{"time":149000,"text":"hypertension, diabetes, obesity, lack of exercise. The usual suspects."},{"time":154000,"text":"Right here in Tanzania, 30 percent of individuals have hypertension."},{"time":160000,"text":"20 percent are getting treated."},{"time":162000,"text":"Only less than one percent are adequately treated."},{"time":165000,"text":"If we can treat hypertension alone in Africa,"},{"time":168000,"text":"we'll save 250,000 lives a year. That's quite significant!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":173000,"text":"Easy to treat. Look at the situation in Mauritius."},{"time":176000,"text":"In eight short years -- we're here talking about HIV, malaria,"},{"time":181000,"text":"which is all good."},{"time":182000,"text":"We cannot make the mistakes we've made with malaria and HIV."},{"time":186000,"text":"In eight short years, non-communicable diseases"},{"time":189000,"text":"will become the leading causes of death in Africa."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193000,"text":"That is something to keep in mind. We can't deal with it with situations like this."},{"time":198000,"text":"This is a typical African hospital. We can't depend on the elites --"},{"time":202000,"text":"they go to USA, Germany, U.K. for treatment. Unbelievable."},{"time":210000,"text":"You can't depend on foreign aid alone."},{"time":212000,"text":"Here is the situation: countries are turning inwards."},{"time":215000,"text":"Post-9/11, [the] United States has had a lot of trouble"},{"time":218000,"text":"to deal with, their own internal issues."},{"time":220000,"text":"So, they spend their money trying to fix those problems."},{"time":224000,"text":"You can't rightly -- it's not their responsibility,"},{"time":227000,"text":"it is my responsibility. I have to take care of my own problems."},{"time":231000,"text":"If they help, that's good! But that is not my expectation."},{"time":236000,"text":"These worsening indices of health care or health studies in Africa"},{"time":239000,"text":"demand a new look. We cannot keep on doing things"},{"time":243000,"text":"the way we've always done them."},{"time":244000,"text":"If they have not worked, we have to look for alternative solutions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":248000,"text":"I'm here to talk to you about solutions."},{"time":250000,"text":"This has been -- what has been a difficult sign to some of us."},{"time":255000,"text":"Several years ago, we started thinking about it."},{"time":258000,"text":"Everyone knows the problem. No one knows what the solutions are."},{"time":262000,"text":"We decided that we needed to put our money where our mouth is."},{"time":267000,"text":"Everyone is ready to throw in money,"},{"time":270000,"text":"in terms of free money aid to developing countries."},{"time":273000,"text":"Talk about sustainable investment, no one is interested."},{"time":277000,"text":"You can't raise money."},{"time":279000,"text":"I have done businesses in healthcare in the United States --"},{"time":282000,"text":"I live in Nashville, Tennessee, health care capital of America."},{"time":285000,"text":"[It's] very easy to raise money for health-care ventures."},{"time":288000,"text":"But start telling them, you know,"},{"time":290000,"text":"we're going to try to do it in Nigeria -- everyone runs away."},{"time":292000,"text":"That is totally wrong. Those of you in the audience here,"},{"time":298000,"text":"if you want to help Africa, invest money in sustainable development."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301000,"text":"Let me lead you through a day in the life of the Heart Institute,"},{"time":305000,"text":"so you get a glimpse of what we do,"},{"time":307000,"text":"and I'll talk a little bit more about it."},{"time":370000,"text":"What we have done is to show that high-quality health care,"},{"time":376000,"text":"comparable to the best anywhere in the world,"},{"time":378000,"text":"can be done in a developing country environment."},{"time":381000,"text":"We have 25 positions right now -- all of them trained,"},{"time":386000,"text":"board certified in the USA, Canada or Britain."},{"time":389000,"text":"We have every modality that can be done in Vanderbilt,"},{"time":393000,"text":"Cleveland Clinic -- everywhere in the U.S. --"},{"time":396000,"text":"and we do it for about 10 percent of the cost"},{"time":399000,"text":"that you will need to do those things in the United States."},{"time":403000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":408000,"text":"Additionally, we have a policy"},{"time":410000,"text":"that no one is ever turned away because of ability to pay."},{"time":414000,"text":"We take care of everyone."},{"time":416000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":417000,"text":"Whether you have one dollar, two dollars -- it doesn't matter."},{"time":420000,"text":"And I will tell you how we're able to do it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":423000,"text":"We make sure that we select our equipment properly."},{"time":427000,"text":"We go for modular units. Units that have multi-modality functions"},{"time":431000,"text":"have modular components. Easy to repair, and because of that,"},{"time":436000,"text":"we do not take things that are not durable and cannot last."},{"time":440000,"text":"We emphasize training,"},{"time":442000,"text":"and we make sure that this process is regenerative."},{"time":445000,"text":"Very soon we will all be dead and gone, but the problems will stay,"},{"time":449000,"text":"unless we have people taking over from where we stopped."}]},{"cues":[{"time":453000,"text":"We made sure that we produced some things ourselves."},{"time":456000,"text":"We do not buy unit doses of radiopharmaceuticals."},{"time":459000,"text":"We get the generators from the companies."},{"time":462000,"text":"We manufacture them in-house, ourselves. That keeps the costs down."},{"time":466000,"text":"So, for a radiopharmaceutical in the U.S. --"},{"time":469000,"text":"that you'll get a unit dose for 250 dollars --"},{"time":472000,"text":"when we're finished manufacturing it in-house,"},{"time":474000,"text":"we come at a price of about two dollars."},{"time":476000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":480000,"text":"We recognize that the only way to bridge the gap"},{"time":483000,"text":"between the rich and poor countries"},{"time":486000,"text":"is through education and technology."},{"time":489000,"text":"All these problems we're talking about --"},{"time":491000,"text":"if we bring development, they will all disappear."},{"time":494000,"text":"Technology is a great equalizer. How do we make it work?"},{"time":499000,"text":"It's been proved: self-care is cost-effective."},{"time":501000,"text":"It extends opportunity to the rural centers,"},{"time":505000,"text":"and we can use expertise in a very smart way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":508000,"text":"This is the way our centers are set up."},{"time":511000,"text":"We currently have three locations in the Caribbean,"},{"time":514000,"text":"and we're planning a fourth one."},{"time":516000,"text":"And we have now decided to go into Africa."},{"time":519000,"text":"We will be doing the West African Heart Institute"},{"time":522000,"text":"in Port Harcourt, Nigeria. That project will be starting"},{"time":525000,"text":"within the next few months. We hope to open in 2008-09."},{"time":529000,"text":"And we will do other centers."},{"time":531000,"text":"This model can be adapted to every disease process."},{"time":535000,"text":"All the units, all the centers, are linked"},{"time":537000,"text":"through a switched hub to a central server,"},{"time":541000,"text":"and all the images are populated to review stations."},{"time":544000,"text":"And we designed this telemedicine solution. It's proprietary to us,"},{"time":549000,"text":"and we are happy to share what we have learned with anyone"},{"time":552000,"text":"who is interested in doing it. You can still be profitable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":557000,"text":"We make sure that the telemedicine platform gives access"},{"time":563000,"text":"to expert medical specialists anywhere in the world,"},{"time":567000,"text":"just by a click of the button."},{"time":569000,"text":"I'll lead you through, to see how this happens."},{"time":572000,"text":"This is at the Heart Institute. The doctors from anywhere can log in."},{"time":576000,"text":"I can call you in Switzerland and say, \"Listen, go into our system."},{"time":580000,"text":"Look at Mrs. Jones. Look at the study, tell me what you think.\""},{"time":584000,"text":"They'll give me that information,"},{"time":586000,"text":"and we'll make the care of the patient better."},{"time":589000,"text":"The patient doesn't have to travel."},{"time":591000,"text":"He doesn't have to experience the anxiety of not knowing"},{"time":594000,"text":"because of limited expertise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":598000,"text":"We also use [an] electronic medical record system."},{"time":601000,"text":"I'm happy to say that the things we have implemented --"},{"time":605000,"text":"80 percent of U.S. practices do not have them, and yet the technology is there."},{"time":612000,"text":"But you know, they have that luxury."},{"time":613000,"text":"Because if you can't get it in Nashville, you can travel to Birmingham,"},{"time":618000,"text":"two hours away, and you'll get it. If you can't get it in Cleveland,"},{"time":621000,"text":"you can go to Cincinnati. We don't have that luxury,"},{"time":624000,"text":"so we have to make it happen."},{"time":626000,"text":"When we do it, we will put the cost of care down."},{"time":630000,"text":"And we'll extend it to the rural centers and make it affordable."},{"time":634000,"text":"And everyone will get the care they deserve."}]},{"cues":[{"time":637000,"text":"It cannot just be technology, we recognize that."},{"time":641000,"text":"Prevention must be part of the solution -- we emphasize that."},{"time":645000,"text":"But, you know, you have to tell people what can be done."},{"time":649000,"text":"It's not possible to tell people to do what is going to be expensive,"},{"time":652000,"text":"and they go home and can't do it."},{"time":655000,"text":"They need to be alive, they need to feed."},{"time":657000,"text":"We recommend exercise as the most effective, simple, easy thing to do."},{"time":663000,"text":"We have had walks every year -- every March, April."},{"time":667000,"text":"We form people into groups and make them go into challenges."},{"time":672000,"text":"Which group loses the most weight, we give them prizes."},{"time":675000,"text":"Which groups record more walking distance by pedometer,"},{"time":679000,"text":"we give them prizes. We do this constantly."},{"time":682000,"text":"We encourage them to bring children."},{"time":684000,"text":"That way we start exposing the children from very early on,"},{"time":687000,"text":"on what these issues are. Because once they learn it,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":691000,"text":"they will stay with it. In doing this we have created"},{"time":695000,"text":"at least 100 skilled jobs in Jamaica alone,"},{"time":698000,"text":"and these are physicians with expertise and special training."},{"time":702000,"text":"We have taken care of over 1,000 indigent patients that could have died,"},{"time":706000,"text":"including four free pacemakers in patients"},{"time":708000,"text":"with complete heart block. For those that understand cardiology,"},{"time":712000,"text":"complete heart block means certain death."},{"time":715000,"text":"If you don't get this pacemaker, you will be dead."},{"time":718000,"text":"So we are pleased with that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":719000,"text":"Indirectly, we have saved the government of Jamaica five million dollars"},{"time":723000,"text":"from people that would have gone to Miami or Atlanta for care."},{"time":728000,"text":"And we've hopefully saved a lot of lives."},{"time":731000,"text":"By the end of this year, we would have contributed over one million dollars"},{"time":736000,"text":"in indigent care. In the first four months, it's been 340,000 dollars,"},{"time":740000,"text":"averaging 85,000 dollars a month. The government will not do that,"},{"time":746000,"text":"because they have competing needs."},{"time":747000,"text":"They need to put resources elsewhere. But we can still do it."},{"time":750000,"text":"People say, \"How can you do that?\" This is how we can do that."},{"time":755000,"text":"At least 4,000 rich Jamaicans that were heading to Miami for treatment"},{"time":760000,"text":"have self-confessed that they did not go to Miami"},{"time":765000,"text":"because of the Heart Institute of the Caribbean."},{"time":767000,"text":"And, if they went to Miami, they will spend significantly more --"},{"time":772000,"text":"eight to 10 times more. And they feel happy spending it at home,"},{"time":777000,"text":"getting the same quality of care."},{"time":778000,"text":"And for that money -- for every one patient that has the money to pay,"},{"time":784000,"text":"it gives us an opportunity to take care of at least four people"},{"time":787000,"text":"that do not have the resources to pay."},{"time":790000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":795000,"text":"For this to work, this progress must be sustainable."},{"time":798000,"text":"So, we emphasize training. Training is critical."},{"time":801000,"text":"We have gone further: we have formed a relationship"},{"time":805000,"text":"with the University of Technology, Jamaica,"},{"time":808000,"text":"where I now have an appointment."},{"time":809000,"text":"And we are starting a biomedical engineering program,"},{"time":812000,"text":"so that we will train people locally, who can repair that equipment."},{"time":817000,"text":"That way we're not going to deal with obsolescence and all those kinds of issues."},{"time":821000,"text":"We're also starting ancillary health-care technology training programs --"},{"time":826000,"text":"training people in echocardiography, cardiac ultrasound,"},{"time":830000,"text":"those kinds of things. Now, with that kind of training,"},{"time":833000,"text":"it gives people motivation."},{"time":835000,"text":"Because now they will get a bachelors degree in medical imaging"},{"time":838000,"text":"and all that kind of stuff. In the process, I want you to just hear"},{"time":844000,"text":"from the trainees themselves what it has meant for them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":848000,"text":"(Video) Dr. Jason Topping: My name is Jason Topping."},{"time":849000,"text":"I'm a senior resident in anesthesia in intensive care"},{"time":852000,"text":"at the University Hospital of the West Indies."},{"time":855000,"text":"I came to the Heart Institute in 2006,"},{"time":858000,"text":"as part of my elective in my anesthesia and intensive care program."},{"time":863000,"text":"I spent three months at the Heart Institute."},{"time":866000,"text":"There's been no doubt around my colleagues"},{"time":868000,"text":"about the utility of the training I received here,"},{"time":871000,"text":"and I think there's been an increased interest now in --"},{"time":876000,"text":"particularly in echocardiography and its use in our setting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":880000,"text":"Sharon Lazarus: I am an echocardiographer at the Heart Institute of the Caribbean,"},{"time":885000,"text":"since the past two years. I received training at this institution."},{"time":890000,"text":"I think this aspect of training in cardiology"},{"time":895000,"text":"that the Heart Institute of the Caribbean has introduced in Jamaica"},{"time":899000,"text":"is very important in terms of diagnosing cardiac diseases."}]},{"cues":[{"time":908000,"text":"Ernest Madu: The lesson in this is that it can be done, and it can be sustained,"},{"time":913000,"text":"and you can make it possible for everyone."},{"time":917000,"text":"Who are we to decide that poor people cannot get the best care?"},{"time":921000,"text":"When have you been appointed to play God?"},{"time":925000,"text":"It is not my decision. My job is to make sure that every person,"},{"time":930000,"text":"no matter what fate has assigned to you, will have the opportunity"},{"time":935000,"text":"to get the best quality health care in life."},{"time":938000,"text":"Next stop is West African Heart Institute,"},{"time":942000,"text":"that we are going to be doing in Port Harcourt, Nigeria,"},{"time":945000,"text":"as I said before. We will do other centers across West Africa."},{"time":949000,"text":"We will extend the same system into other areas,"},{"time":954000,"text":"like dialysis treatment."},{"time":955000,"text":"And anyone who is interested in doing it in any health care situation,"},{"time":959000,"text":"we will be happy to assist you and tell you how we've done it,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":964000,"text":"and how you can do it. If we do this,"},{"time":968000,"text":"we can change the face of health care in Africa."},{"time":972000,"text":"Africa has been good to us; it is time for us to give back to Africa."},{"time":976000,"text":"I am going. Those who want to come,"},{"time":979000,"text":"I welcome you to come along with me."},{"time":981000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":983000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}